## Test Flow Diagram

```
Test Execution
      │
      ├─→ Initialize Factory
      │   └─→ Create WebApiFactory instance
      │   └─→ Create HttpClient
      │   └─→ POST /reset-database
      │
      ├─→ Execute Test
      │   ├─→ Arrange (Setup test data)
      │   ├─→ Act (Call endpoint)
      │   └─→ Assert (Verify response)
      │
      └─→ Cleanup
          ├─→ HttpClient.Dispose()
          └─→ Factory.DisposeAsync()
```

---

## Request/Response Pattern

### Success Response (201 Created)
```
Request:  POST /meals
Body:     { "name": "...", "description": "...", "price": 150.00 }
Response: 201 Created
Headers:  Location: /meals/3
```

### Error Response (400 Bad Request)
```
Request:  POST /menu-items
Body:     { "mealId": 999, "date": "2024-04-20", "availablePortions": 10 }
Response: 400 Bad Request
Body:     "Selected meal does not exist."
```

### Not Found Response (404)
```
Request:  GET /meals/999
Response: 404 Not Found
```

